Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(450,0)}反擊 的 處刑台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.04,0:02:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 所殺的人數已記不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒人會去數刷牙吃飯的次數
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.52,0:02:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Geass適合暗殺 聽別人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.58,0:02:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才殺人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒別的地方可待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,潛入工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.18,0:02:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演弟弟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.89,0:03:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從未見過父母親人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 若這是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.53,0:03:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的哥哥就是魯路修·蘭佩洛奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的Geass是停止時間的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒理由回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接到的指令是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.36,0:03:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若魯路修·蘭佩洛奇記憶恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.32,0:03:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若ZERO復活 就將其抹殺
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,16 17 18 19…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.95,0:03:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,435)\fs22}這數字是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從你出現時起 我就在心裡計算時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但現在數字有偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為是什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將成為尋找娜娜莉的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 你停止的並非時間
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是我身體所感受到的時間而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.42,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算明白這個也贏不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 誰也不能度過和我相同的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 你是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有立即殺了我 就是因為你很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 兩樣東西都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.53,0:04:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.37,0:04:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個是你們以我為誘餌正在追尋的C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你能放過我 我就把C.C.給你揪出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要出賣C.C.嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的性命最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另一個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.89,0:04:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 未來是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.66,0:04:39.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來就是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.55,0:04:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任務前方有希望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住了C.C. 你能開拓出怎樣的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持現狀而已 一成不變
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是任務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.74,0:04:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺了我 就完不成任務
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想抓住C.C.吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天 我會把C.C.揪出來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣你就能抓住嶄新的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題 我不會說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有對你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.37,0:05:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我想起青森來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比那好點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少全員都穿了衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO對總領事下了Geass吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.61,0:05:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:24.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過在此失手的話 我們和魯路修就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又支離破碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.38,0:05:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.49,0:05:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟獨自前來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.41,0:05:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中華聯邦的總領事應該已經承認日本合眾國了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位大人即將去世
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:40.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色騎士團要選擇在此毀滅一途嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.78,0:05:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 突然說這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.55,0:05:49.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當總領事在我們手中光榮殉職好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.36,0:05:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO似乎點燃了意外的導火索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.36,0:05:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是遠大的理想 還是庸俗的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姑且爭取到了讓羅洛等待的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能得到C.C. 他就會隱瞞我恢復記憶的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 他的根本目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不是在布里塔尼亞陞遷或對其效忠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 該尋找別的線索嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.32,0:06:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖是危險的牌 但有相應的價值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間躊躇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天籐堂他們就會被處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.67,0:06:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的Geass已暴露給羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想辦法殺了羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:34.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記憶恢復的事也會被機情知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.69,0:06:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.89,0:06:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在救出娜娜莉之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.76,0:06:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有繼續假裝學生了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好 吉爾弗德等人似乎和機情聯繫不深
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隱藏的Knightmare未被發現也能說明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但僅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.69,0:06:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出黑色騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.67,0:06:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時除去羅洛的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那小鬼殺了布魯諾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第五人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.30,0:07:14.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維克多也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.26,0:07:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過碰到了他的掛墜盒就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.11,0:07:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人平時就有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.33,0:07:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不至於被殺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自稱ZERO的人都出現了 我們必須更團結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟殺害同伴的死神 要怎麼組隊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.05,0:07:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重點是任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.50,0:07:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要什麼同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活的ZERO是那個ZERO嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.14,0:07:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是哪個 都會再度拋棄我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總領事館的爆炸事件原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今還沒有官方說明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有聯絡說認可執行處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處刑不過是以儆傚尤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.27,0:07:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我來說是低級的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會出現嗎 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出來的話也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無意引發奇跡的ZERO 也得不到民眾支持
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您連這一步都想到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.77,0:08:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我希望他出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是祈禱他出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.57,0:08:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不知身在何處的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.89,0:08:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您為何承認日本合眾國
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還未向朱禁城確認就獨斷專行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是大宦官之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.45,0:08:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這行為也不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使您打算利用ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎可利用ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有ZERO才有幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.02,0:08:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖上的聖意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.55,0:08:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種小丫頭哪比得上ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.69,0:08:47.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO會賜予我幸福才是絕對的法則
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.81,0:08:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這賣國賊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.49,0:08:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅天已死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:00.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論殺害 情報操作還是偽裝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走哪條路羅洛都是瓶頸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.26,0:09:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,處刑開始之前必須想辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.38,0:09:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到那情報的證據
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去曾自稱黑色騎士團
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.23,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擾亂11區的恐怖分子的處刑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在即將執行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO會現身於部下的刑場之上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.11,0:09:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO大人 求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救籐堂將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別殺他們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO背叛了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不會來救我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他一定會來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.36,0:09:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要那是本人 只要他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.92,0:09:47.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會來引發奇跡的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別放鬆警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但C.C.也有可能出現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.53,0:10:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇要…這下就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來吧 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.01,0:10:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親安德列斯·達爾頓的仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.51,0:10:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大部隊發來機密指令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為防止通信竊聽 命屬下口頭傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身份 我暫借一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這該怎麼理解才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:33.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若ZERO出現 只管行動便是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算我們對布里塔尼亞開炮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.95,0:10:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也可以裝作一無所知？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這交易不算壞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說你是武官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來搞政治也挺有一套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.71,0:10:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金梅爾卿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.90,0:10:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先行量產機沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.23,0:10:51.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機情使用過 說不定會有奇怪的壞習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.85,0:10:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是重要的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.10,0:10:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一點不對勁就立即報告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.00,0:10:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是金梅爾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vincent無異常 可以出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.86,0:11:05.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不遵守約定 就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.13,0:11:07.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 終於到了處刑時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.82,0:11:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色騎士團殘黨即將接受正義的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.10,0:11:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.07,0:11:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請顯示奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.43,0:11:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,11區人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.90,0:11:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們所相信的ZERO沒有現身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是騙局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他逃避了我提出的堂堂正正的決鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉槍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.33,0:11:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:37.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從這裡出去你也會被殺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已做得夠好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了 吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.90,0:11:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他來了 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也無法出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦 憑你一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.13,0:11:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:59.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繞到後面了嗎 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉爾弗德 你即將處刑的不是恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:11.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我合眾國軍 黑色騎士團的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要我根據國際法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.84,0:12:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承認他們是俘虜？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.81,0:12:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 若打破了與我的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.18,0:12:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就要死 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.74,0:12:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 魯路修·蘭佩洛奇
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.22,0:12:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO現身了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:39.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多麼愚蠢的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.39,0:12:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.57,0:12:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是本人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用說嗎 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.73,0:12:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有公佈處刑的事 但沒有更多報導啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.83,0:12:51.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO只有一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然乘在Knightmare Frame上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.36,0:12:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的應該不是自首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.25,0:12:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是若打算獨自一人作戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 我說的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 就按去年的計劃行事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那得等ZERO先渡過這難關才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑世子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了今後的打算 先開始進行那個準備吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞軍方面已開始…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.01,0:13:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有羅洛跟著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半小時前就進了螺旋劇場
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.38,0:13:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久違了 吉爾弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出來敘敘舊如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.91,0:13:31.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙邀請 不過請容我謝絕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的因緣 讓我以Knightmare來回應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出來就無法使用Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.20,0:13:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你的風格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼來確定規則吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:43.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規則？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.37,0:13:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決鬥的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.68,0:13:48.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥要一對一做個了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我不會讓別人插手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.87,0:13:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.24,0:13:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.53,0:13:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的武器是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.39,0:14:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 讓我借那面盾一用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.36,0:14:03.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.37,0:14:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鎮壓暴動用的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.66,0:14:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會 一開始就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.49,0:14:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算自我了斷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人失望 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.74,0:14:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.88,0:14:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能解決一隻寄生蟲大宦官 算是欠他個人情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:25.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這不是基於永續調和的盟約
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若ZERO無能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只得讓黑色騎士團變成外交的工具了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.18,0:14:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提個問題 吉爾弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若有正義無法擊敗的邪惡存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.79,0:14:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會如何做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不惜玷污雙手以惡制惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:46.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是寧可捨身取義 也要將自己的正義貫徹到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何 留存下來的終究是邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.00,0:14:51.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矛盾 文字遊戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.56,0:14:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的正義與公主殿下同在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.08,0:14:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是我 不惜化身為邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.73,0:14:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要擊殺極惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,YES Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.85,0:15:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這作戰是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.01,0:15:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色叛亂時的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.97,0:15:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第12步兵部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去第4等級的階層控制室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的部下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.58,0:15:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指揮突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.58,0:15:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自在戰鬥裝甲機部隊跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救出扇先生等人為最優先事項
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.90,0:15:40.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,α4呼叫α1 請回答 α1 α1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.37,0:15:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 有人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:44.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.63,0:15:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼一對一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.61,0:15:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.61,0:16:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色騎士團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.10,0:16:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人已落入我國領土內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.92,0:16:05.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快摧毀布里塔尼亞軍 拯救同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同胞…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:10.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反過來利用了租界構造嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.68,0:16:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 在布里塔尼亞重整態勢之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被他們逃進中華聯邦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.29,0:16:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的目的歸根到底是C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊交給吉爾弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.70,0:16:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.34,0:16:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡已經是日本的領土了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才討厭布里塔尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永別了 11區的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.99,0:16:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擋住了？在這個距離
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是輻射波動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近身後我的勝利就已成定局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.47,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.82,0:17:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟敢把阿爾弗雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開槍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是中華聯邦的治外法權區
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.50,0:17:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有媒體的攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.46,0:17:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vincent
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vincent突擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這邊不能動 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.82,0:17:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎 羅洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交出C.C.的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.63,0:17:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修 一開始就欺騙了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.89,0:17:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不行 還不能被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說要給我未來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能死在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:56.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要完成任務 就有未來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物理現象停止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接命中線路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟在這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 戴維德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.30,0:18:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若打中總領事館 就要跟中華聯邦開戰了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.32,0:18:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 你是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.15,0:18:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是被移植的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.65,0:18:38.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你共同度過的那段時間 並無虛假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止的生活 不是虛假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.34,0:18:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.84,0:18:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 沒有生日的我第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.57,0:18:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到那個
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明說了 自己的性命最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.84,0:19:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻為了那種無聊的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為約好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.00,0:19:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的嶄新未來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的未來 和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.82,0:19:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO 在此了斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.18,0:19:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃我一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.78,0:19:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這鐵錘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.85,0:19:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思 金梅爾卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 你是ZERO的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.88,0:19:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魯路修死了任務就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.54,0:19:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.83,0:19:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.96,0:19:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是維蕾塔老師打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用IMOpen（即時通信公開線路）連接
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.52,0:19:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛嗎 你去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.16,0:19:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:52.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.93,0:19:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上個廁所好歹讓我們分別解決啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.57,0:19:57.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 剛才怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.03,0:19:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總領事館的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好像很轟動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 若之前的事被知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.60,0:20:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會被機情局處決
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.28,0:20:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.15,0:20:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓弟弟捲進危險的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是當然的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅洛不適合殺人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.13,0:20:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此為止 布里塔尼亞的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更進一步的行動將視為武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.64,0:20:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扇先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝 卡蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,籐堂先生你們也…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 給你添麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.67,0:20:45.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受苦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:47.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那台Knightmare呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:54.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道 那架機體本是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.34,0:20:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的機師我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他保護了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.40,0:21:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少不是敵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明C.C.就在眼前 我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一開始 在布里塔尼亞就沒有安寧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.82,0:21:10.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歸宿 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,落網了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把這種資料留在司令室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說明除了Geass以外一無所長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這玩意裡的密碼竟能派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.01,0:21:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,模式D
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.44,0:21:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 ZERO的機體取這個軌道時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:33.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從後方攻擊追逐他的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.46,0:21:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後若ZERO逃出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.58,0:21:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就把對方的Knightmare完全破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不逃出的話 就原地待機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.46,0:21:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將娜娜莉取而代之的冒牌貨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.42,0:21:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我搾乾你的每一滴血
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.42,0:21:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再像破抹布一樣拋棄
